[[利吉丹島|利吉丹島]]和[[西巴丹島|西巴丹島]]是位於馬來西亞[[沙巴|沙巴]]東南沿海[[西里伯斯海|西里伯斯海]]上的兩座島嶼。自1969年以來，印尼和馬來西亞不斷就兩島嶼的主權產生[[領土糾紛|爭議]]，而該爭端於1991年印尼發現馬來西亞於西巴丹島上建造旅遊設施後加劇。<ref name="facility">{{cite web|url=https://www.dur.ac.uk/ibru/publications/view/?id=209|title=The Territorial Dispute between Indonesia and Malaysia over Pulau Sipadan and Pulau Ligitan in the Celebes Sea: a Study in International Law|author=Renate Haller-Trost|publisher=[[杜倫大學|Durham University]]|year=1995|accessdate=2016-02-07|language=en|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322044152/https://www.dur.ac.uk/ibru/publications/view/?id=209|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Rosenne2003">{{cite book|author=Shabtai Rosenne|title=The World Court: What it is and how it Works|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qLoGGCHESvsC&pg=PA223|year=2003|publisher=United Nations Publications|isbn=978-90-04-13816-2|pages=223–|language=en}}</ref>印尼聲稱曾於1969年與馬來西亞達成口頭協議，但馬來西亞否認兩國之間有過協議，堅稱兩島嶼屬於其沙巴領土的一部分<ref name="facility"/>，且兩國當時並未在該地區劃定{{tsl|en|Maritime boundary|海上邊界}}，也未要求法院就此事作出進一步裁決。<ref name="Rosenne2003"/>1998年11月2日，兩國同意將此爭議提交[[國際法院|國際法院]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.icj-cij.org/docket/?pr=330&code=inma&p1=3&p2=3&p3=6&case=102&k=df|title=Indonesia and Malaysia jointly bring dispute over islands to the International Court of Justice|publisher=International Court of Justice|date=1998-11-02|accessdate=2016-02-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305143826/http://www.icj-cij.org/docket/?pr=330&code=inma&p1=3&p2=3&p3=6&case=102&k=df|archivedate=2016-03-05|dead-url=yes|language=en}}</ref>

=== 菲律賓加入 ===
[[菲律賓|菲律賓]]在訴訟期間以該國對{{tsl|en|North Borneo dispute|北婆羅洲領土爭端|北婆羅洲的主權聲索}}為由申請參加兩島嶼的訴訟案。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.icj-cij.org/docket/files/102/7179.pdf|title=Case Concerning Sovereignty over Pulau Ligitan and Pulau Sipadan [Indonesia/Malaysia] (Application for Permission to Intervene by the Government of the Philippines)|publisher=International Court of Justice|date=2001-03-13|accessdate=2016-02-07|format=PDF|language=en|archive-date=2016-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207102423/http://www.icj-cij.org/docket/files/102/7179.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>菲律賓方面宣稱，曾統治當地的[[蘇祿蘇丹國|蘇祿蘇丹國]]已於1962年將[[北婆羅洲|北婆羅洲]]（今沙巴）主權轉讓予菲律賓<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.officialgazette.gov.ph/1962/04/24/cession-and-transfer-of-the-territory-of-north-borneo-by-his-highness-sultan-mohammad-esmail-kiram-sultan-of-sulu-acting-with-the-consent-and-aprroval-of-the-ruma-bechara-in-council-assembled-to/|title=Cession and transfer of the territory of North Borneo by His Highness, Sultan Mohammad Esmail Kiram, Sultan of Sulu, acting with the consent and approval of the Ruma Bechara, in council assembled, to the Republic of the Philippines|publisher=Government of the Philippines|date=1962-04-24|accessdate=2016-02-07|language=en|archive-date=2017-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171111120528/http://www.officialgazette.gov.ph/1962/04/24/cession-and-transfer-of-the-territory-of-north-borneo-by-his-highness-sultan-mohammad-esmail-kiram-sultan-of-sulu-acting-with-the-consent-and-aprroval-of-the-ruma-bechara-in-council-assembled-to/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在[[聯合國|聯合國]]於1963年組織的{{tsl|en|Cobbold Commission|科博爾德委員會|公民投票}}中，當地的多數居民選擇成為馬來西亞的一部分，而非菲律賓。<ref name="Rosenne2003"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://treaties.un.org/doc/publication/unts/volume%20750/volume-750-i-10760-english.pdf|title=United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland and Federation of Malaya, North Borneo, Sarawak and Singapore (Agreement relating to Malaysia)|publisher=[[United_Nations|United Nations]]|year=1963|accessdate=2015-09-13|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913021746/https://treaties.un.org/doc/publication/unts/volume%20750/volume-750-i-10760-english.pdf|archivedate=2015-09-13|dead-url=yes|format=PDF|language=en}}</ref>菲律賓的參加動機亦受到國際法院質疑，即該國是否與印尼和馬來西亞一樣都具有「足夠龐大的法律利益」。2001年6月，法院在舉行口頭[[聽證會|聽證會]]後，最終以14票對1票的表決結果駁回了菲律賓的申請，理由為該國提出的請求與本案件無關。<ref>{{Cite web|title=国际法院的报告|url=https://www.icj-cij.org/public/files/annual-reports/2001-2002-ch.pdf|accessdate=2020-11-13|author=|date=2002-09-06|format=PDF|work=International Court of Justice|publisher=United Nation|pages=44|language=zh-hans|issn=0251-8503|location=紐約|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113154116/https://www.icj-cij.org/public/files/annual-reports/2001-2002-ch.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Rosenne2003"/>

== 判決 ==
利吉丹島和西巴丹島起初被認為是[[無主地|無主地]]，但由於馬來西亞的原殖民母國[[大英帝國|英國]]與印尼的原殖民母國[[荷蘭帝國|荷蘭]]相比，在馬來西亞建國後積極開發兩島嶼，因此國際法院以此為由，根據「有效佔領」狀況判決兩島嶼歸屬於馬來西亞。<ref name="awarded"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2013/01/30/are-we-losing-more-islands-after-sipadan-ligitan-dispute.html|title=Are we losing more islands after Sipadan-Ligitan dispute?|author=Made Andi Arsana|publisher=[[雅加達郵報|The Jakarta Post]]|date=2013-01-30|accessdate=2016-02-07|language=en|archive-date=2016-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160207034229/http://www.thejakartapost.com/news/2013/01/30/are-we-losing-more-islands-after-sipadan-ligitan-dispute.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>此外，利、西兩島嶼的位置較靠近馬來西亞，馬來西亞擁有的最早文件是1878年英國與[[蘇祿蘇丹國|蘇祿蘇丹國]]簽訂的協議，將蘇祿地區納入[[英屬婆羅洲|英屬婆羅洲]]；而印尼的要求主要是基於1891年英國與荷蘭簽署的邊界條約。<ref name="Rosenne2003"/>

